Welcome to this node manager pod, common commands:
 - Show version                       fireeth --version

Node manager commands (eth-... <tab> to show all):
 - Check if running                   eth-is-running

 - Geth: Check if syncing             geth-is-syncing
 - Geth: Check if has peers           geth-has-peers
 - Geth: List peers                   geth-list-peers
 - Geth: verbosity level              geth-debug <1-10>
 - Attach to Geth instance            geth attach /sf-data/*/ipc (See https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/Management-APIs#list-of-management-apis)

 - Take a volume snapshot             eth-volume-snapshot
 - Debug Deep Mind logs for 30s       eth-debug-firehose-logs-30s
 - Stop instance                      eth-maintenance
 - Start or restart instance          eth-resume

